 performed with the EMPIRE code. The spherical optical model      1125 1451
 provided total cross sections and neutron scattering,            1125 1451
 Hauser-Feshbach statistical model described the bulk of particle 1125 1451
 emission, and the exciton pre-equilibrium model described major  1125 1451
 features of fast particle emission at higher incident energies.  1125 1451
